description:
• Be the awesome SAP Solution Architect : Learn in and out of SAP Technology
  • For the executive: what SAP is and how it can help you.
  • For the practitioner: details on governance, architecture, troubleshooting, security and using SAP with the best practices
  • For everyone: the latest and best tips and tricks on SAP Technology.
  • Get the Architect overview of how to secure an SAP system.
  • The program is planned keeping SAP Architect job in mind.
title: SAP Architect
instructors: SAP Training Now & OJAYO SAP education university
